00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,520
A pipe dream?

289
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:06,430
You were right.

290
00:14:06,920 --> 00:14:08,120
He is the evil cultivator

291
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:10,280
that Feng Xiang and I met

