00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:11,640
when we built the Immortals Array 6,000 years ago,

293
00:14:11,950 --> 00:14:13,160
and he has really lived for so long.

294
00:14:14,470 --> 00:14:15,190
He was trying

295
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:16,760
to seize the Chaos Pearl

296
00:14:17,190 --> 00:14:19,160
