300
00:14:24,430 --> 00:14:25,400
and survived all these years

301
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:26,640
by changing his face.

302
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:28,430
However,

303
00:14:29,040 --> 00:14:30,590
why did you suspect

304
00:14:30,830 --> 00:14:31,760
He Xianwo had lived long?

305
00:14:33,190 --> 00:14:34,830
He knows how to break the Immortals Array,

306
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,310
so I'm guessing

307
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,400
that when you built it back then,

308
00:14:38,640 --> 00:14:40,160
he was probably snooping around

309
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,920
and learning the key to the array.

310
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:43,360
And not long ago,

311
00:14:43,830 --> 00:14:45,040
he refined the Illusion Elixir.

312
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:48,280
