314
00:14:49,950 --> 00:14:51,190
of Phoenix Mountain

315
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,950
6,000 years ago.

316
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,710
It's true that he couldn't have gotten it

317
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:57,160
if he hadn't existed

318
00:14:57,520 --> 00:14:58,640
6,000 years ago or more.

319
00:15:00,950 --> 00:15:02,070
But what I am puzzled about is

320
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:03,640
that even if a human cultivator

321
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:05,280
reaches the Spiritual Form stage,

322
00:15:05,710 --> 00:15:07,470
his lifespan is only a thousand years at most.

323
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:09,280
Feng Xiang paid such a huge price

324
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,590
to get immortality,

325
00:15:11,790 --> 00:15:13,550
