343
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:50,160
I think this guy

344
00:15:51,070 --> 00:15:53,240
has this evil skill.

345
00:15:53,590 --> 00:15:54,950
What on earth

346
00:15:56,710 --> 00:15:58,360
