368
00:16:40,520 --> 00:16:41,070
life,

369
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:42,590
and death

370
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:44,310
to complete it.

371
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:47,550
Thanks, Qian Guang

372
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,040
