381
00:17:07,270 --> 00:17:08,320
In Snow City, Xuantian Sect,

382
00:17:08,320 --> 00:17:09,420
Mirage Palace, Jade Sky Palace,

383
00:17:09,420 --> 00:17:10,160
and even the Dark Abyss,

384
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,380
the older generation of Saints in the Spiritual Form stage

385
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,190
