387
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:17,560
are me,

388
00:17:18,360 --> 00:17:19,270
Mu Xuanling,

389
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:20,600
and

390
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:22,190
you.

391
00:17:23,080 --> 00:17:24,230
So since then,

392
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:26,600
I have not been plotting against you,

393
00:17:27,990 --> 00:17:29,840
