448
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:29,560
If I die,

449
00:20:30,230 --> 00:20:31,400
you won't get the medicine,

450
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,430
and you'll die too.

451
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,510
Finally,

452
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:41,080
everyone's in.

453
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:45,510
Everyone?

454
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,710
Nan Xuyue.

455
00:20:47,950 --> 00:20:48,560
Open the array.

456
00:20:49,990 --> 00:20:50,670
OK.

457
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,990
As you wish.

